OL,4,Cindefinite strike amid row over jobs
OL,5,Cand pay
OL,7,FNearly 400 council bin workers in
OL,8,FBirmingham have walked out
OL,9,Findefinitely as part of an escalating
OL,10,Fdispute over jobs and pay.
OL,12,FThe Unite union has warned bin
OL,13,Fdisruption in the city could stretch
OL,14,Finto the summer after refuse workers
OL,15,Fvoted in favour of extending their
OL,16,Fstrike mandate over the council's use
OL,17,Fof temporary labour to "undermine"
OL,18,Ftheir industrial action.
