OL,7,FUnite said its members face pay cuts
OL,8,Fafter the scrapping of waste
OL,9,Fcollection and recycling officer
OL,10,Froles, despite already voluntarily
OL,11,Faccepting cuts to pay and terms and
OL,12,Fconditions after the council declared
OL,13,Fbankruptcy.
OL,15,FThe union's national lead officer,
OL,16,FOnay Kasab, said: "The council could
OL,17,Fend this dispute tomorrow by agreeing
OL,18,Fto pay a decent rate of pay.
