OL,7,F"Disruption to Birmingham's refuse
OL,8,Fservice will further deteriorate but
OL,9,Fthis is the fault of a heartless
OL,10,Fcouncil which has slashed pay without
OL,11,Fa thought to the effect it is having
OL,12,Fon workers and their families."
