OL,7,FBirmingham City Council has issued
OL,8,Fadvice to residents saying that they
OL,9,Fshould still put household waste out
OL,10,Fon your normal collection day, and
OL,11,Fthat the council will collect this as
OL,12,Fsoon as possible.
OL,14,FRecycling collections are suspended
OL,15,Fevery day and residents are being
OL,16,Fasked not to put their recycling out
OL,17,Ffor collection.
OL,19,FZoe Mayou, Unite regional officer,
OL,20,Fspoke to ITV Central earlier today at
OL,21,Fa demonstration.
